        "title": "川普應該考慮的兩個處理伊朗戰爭後果的好點子",
        "url": "https://nypost.com/2026/03/22/opinion/2-great-ideas-on-how-to-deal-with-the-iran-war-consequences-that-trump-should-consider/",
